                     <interp inst="t18441021-2579-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 pair of shoes, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of the <persName id="t18441021-name-1096" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18441021-name-1096" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
